  "texts": [
    "Researchers have even developed deep learningbased systems that leverage photoplethysmography (PPG) to authenticate users based on their physiological signals.Behavioral biometrics, on the other hand, focus on identifying and measuring distinctive patterns in human activities to provide continuous and user-friendly security.",
    "These patterns can be used to authenticate users based on their behavioral traits, adding an extra layer of protection.• Intelligent device authentication-which ensures the security of machine-to-machine communication.",
    "By authenticating devices based on their credentials or behavior within the network, AI can enhance the overall security posture.",
    "In fields like cyber-physical systems and the automotive industry, researchers are actively investigating techniques for identifying and authenticating sensors.",
    "They are dedicated to developing methods that ensure accurate identification and authentication of sensors, thereby enhancing the security and reliability of these systems."
  ]
}